Find Walktrap Community and Draw it

com <- walktrap.community(g)
modularity(com)
## [1] 0.8240069
member <- membership(com)
colors <-rainbow(10, .8, .8, alpha=.8)[member]
plot(g, layout=l3, vertex.color=colors, edge.arrow.size=.1, vertex.label.color="black")
